<h1>Ranter</h1>
<p>Hey! The point of Ranter is to just talk about what ever you want, anonymously
just create a password and you're done! No emails or usernames.</p><br/><br/>

<h3>//Threads//</h3>
<table>
<% @posts.each do |post| %>
  <% cycle('odd', 'even') %>
  <tr><td><%= post.body[0..50] + " (" + post.responses.size.to_s + ")" %></td><td><%= link_to "show", :controller => "Posts", :action => "show", :id => post.id %></td></tr>
<% end %>

</table><br/>

<%= link_to "New Thread", :controller => "Posts", :action => "new" %>
